### Test 1: Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "TestPass123!",
  "full_name": "Test User"
}

### Test 2: Login with the user
POST http://localhost:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=test@example.com&password=TestPass123!

### Test 3: Get profile (AFTER LOGIN - copy token from response above)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Test 4: Check email availability
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/check-email/test@example.com

### Test 5: Check username availability
GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/check-username/testuser